entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've begun your adventures in Star Wars Galaxies. It may be a dark path you begin on, but what you do from here is up to you. This is your story!
entries.journal_entry_description: Han has contacted you about your Imperial abduction on Tansarii station. Apparently Jabba has taken notice of this and thinks you would make a good henchman. Jabba doesn't exactly hire people, if you don't work for him he will turn you in to the Empire. Han wants you to meet with his friend Vourk who he says may have a plan to help you get out of this situation.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Something is again jamming Han Solo's communication attempts.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: I think Jabba's on to me. I can't risk making contact like this, but Jabba's after you to work for him too, now. Meet my friend Vourk at the starport, he'll tell you what's going on.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Han says Jabba is looking for you and his friend Vourk can help you out. It would be a good idea to talk to Vourk before Jabba's men find you.
